In summary, the study reported herein has provided insight into the vibrational energy redistribution processes occurring in MA (a sunscreen precursor) immediately after photoexcitation with UV radiation. The LIF and quantum beats provide insight into the Franck-Condon activity of the S1 ← S0 transition, as well as the relative geometries of the S1 and \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
